        {"title": "编写带yield的fixture", "description": "编写一个使用yield的fixture，实现setup和teardown。", "instructions": "请编写Python代码", "exercise_type": "code", "difficulty": "medium", "category": "fixture机制", "knowledge_point": "yield fixture", "code_template": "import pytest\n\n# 编写带yield的fixture\n", "solution": "import pytest\n\n@pytest.fixture\ndef db_connection():\n    # setup\n    connection = {'status': 'connected'}\n    yield connection\n    # teardown\n    connection['status'] = 'disconnected'\n\ndef test_query(db_connection):\n    assert db_connection['status'] == 'connected'", "hint": "yield之前是setup，之后是teardown"},
